<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:smil="http://www.w3.org/2005/SMIL21/BasicAnimation"
	xmlns:ev="http://www.w3.org/2001/xml-events"
	xmlns:xf="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms"
>
	<head>
		<title>Test SMIL</title>
	  <link rel="stylesheet" href="default.css" type="text/css" />
		<script src="http://ubiquity-backplane.googlecode.com/svn/tags/0.2.1/ubiquity-loader.js" type="text/javascript">/**/</script>
	</head>
	<body>
	  <div class="panel" id="panel">
			<div class="lipsum" id="content">
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Nullam odio. Cras 
				tincidunt nulla sed magna. Proin consectetuer rhoncus mi. Sed tincidunt. 
				Pellentesque semper convallis libero. In in nibh. Aenean condimentum risus 
				tempor mauris. Cras et nibh. Donec at leo sed ligula tincidunt ornare. Ut id 
				dui ac metus semper aliquet. Suspendisse sed nisl. Curabitur dictum dignissim 
				purus. Ut mattis posuere justo. Pellentesque nisl velit, malesuada nec, 
				ullamcorper eu, bibendum vitae, risus. Aenean placerat tincidunt orci. Maecenas 
				placerat erat varius mi. Nunc in est in libero vestibulum laoreet. Etiam 
				libero. Phasellus ac leo.
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="hidden">
			I was hidden
		</div>
		<div>
			<xf:trigger>
				<xf:label>Animate</xf:label>
				<xf:action ev:event="DOMActivate">
					<smil:animate targetElement="panel" attributeName="width" to="200" dur="3" repeatCount="indefinite"></smil:animate>
					<smil:animate targetElement="panel" attributeName="height" to="300" dur="1" repeatCount="3" fill="freeze"></smil:animate>
					<smil:animate targetElement="panel" attributeName="left" to="300" dur="1" repeatCount="1" fill="freeze"></smil:animate>
				  <smil:animateColor targetElement="content" attributeName="backgroundColor" to="#ffff00" from="#ccc" dur="0.5" repeatCount="10"></smil:animateColor>
				  <smil:animateColor targetElement="content" attributeName="color" to="#00ffff" from="#ccc" dur="0.5" fill="freeze" repeatCount="10"></smil:animateColor>
					<smil:set attributeName="display" targetElement="hidden" to="block" fill="freeze"></smil:set>
				</xf:action>
			</xf:trigger>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>